  <brief_title>Effect of Lateral Pharyngoplasty on Blood Pressure in Obstructive Sleep Apnea (OSA) Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Lateral Pharyngoplasty on Blood Pressure in Obstructive Sleep Apnea Patients</official_title>
